♪ Ohh la ooh la ♪

01:30.757 --> 01:32.425
♪ I know you know it's coming ♪

01:32.467 --> 01:34.552
♪ Babe try to stop me ♪

01:34.594 --> 01:36.596
♪ Why ♪

01:36.638 --> 01:38.223
♪ Why you looking oh at me ♪

01:38.264 --> 01:39.766
Make the right offer, Gray.

01:41.685 --> 01:44.020
Before this turns
into a bidding war.

01:46.648 --> 01:47.774
Okay Jack.

01:47.816 --> 01:49.317
How did you get her?

01:49.359 --> 01:50.443
Dean hasn't exhibited for years.

01:50.485 --> 01:52.570
What did you say?

01:52.612 --> 01:54.656
Trade secrets,
Marie, trade secrets.

01:54.698 --> 01:57.158
Well perhaps you could work
your magic on your father.

01:57.200 --> 01:58.868
I'd love to know
what he's doing.

02:00.161 --> 02:01.663
Wouldn't we all?

02:06.626 --> 02:07.460
Ruth.

02:08.877 --> 02:11.464
I thought we agreed you
weren't coming tonight.

02:11.506 --> 02:14.509
I hate to tell you what a
great job you're doing here.

02:16.803 --> 02:18.263
Yeah I think we've
done pretty well.

02:18.304 --> 02:19.848
You should enjoy it.

02:19.889 --> 02:21.599
Really enjoy it.

02:21.641 --> 02:22.851
Because it's over.

02:24.477 --> 02:25.353
Sorry, what?

02:27.397 --> 02:29.024
My family is selling
the gallery, Jack.

02:32.694 --> 02:34.154
What did you think, Jack?

02:34.195 --> 02:36.448
You'll just carry on managing
the gallery indefinitely?

02:36.489 --> 02:38.783
We are divorced.

02:38.825 --> 02:41.036
At least we will be when
you sign the papers.

02:41.077 --> 02:44.289
This gallery is my home, Ruth.

02:44.330 --> 02:45.707
I've put everything into it.

02:45.749 --> 02:47.334
Everything except money.

02:50.587 --> 02:51.421
Okay.

02:53.506 --> 02:54.549
I'll buy the gallery.

02:54.591 --> 02:57.177
(chuckling) Did you
win the lottery?

02:59.346 --> 03:01.431
I could maybe sell
the old Italian house

03:02.766 --> 03:03.600
with my dad.

03:04.893 --> 03:06.019
The deserted barn no
one's allowed to mention,

03:06.061 --> 03:07.020
let alone visit?

03:08.188 --> 03:10.523
Your dad's a selfish prick

03:10.565 --> 03:12.442
who's never even
been to your gallery.

03:14.361 --> 03:16.529
He'll never sell that
place and you know it.

03:19.074 --> 03:20.700
Stick to the lottery plan, Jack.

03:22.243 --> 03:23.370
I'll give you a month.

03:26.122 --> 03:29.000
♪ Ooh la ooh la ♪

03:29.042 --> 03:30.669
♪ No money in my pocket ♪

03:30.710 --> 03:33.672
♪ Nothing's gonna
stop this feeling ♪

03:33.713 --> 03:35.006
Robert Foster here.

03:35.048 --> 03:36.424
You know what to do.

03:36.466 --> 03:38.343
Dad, me again.

03:38.385 --> 03:39.844
I'm on my way,
I'll be 20 minutes.

03:39.886 --> 03:41.513
